{"arkId":"cl010104392","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010104392","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Montre et ch\u00e2telaine","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Montre et ch\u00e2telaine"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Louis XV (1715-1774) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque moderne = Ancien R\u00e9gime-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1770","currentLocation":"non expos\u00e9","room":"","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1770,"endYear":"","imprecision":"","text":"3e tiers du XVIIIe si\u00e8cle = dernier tiers du XVIIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Dufour, Pierre","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"","place":"Gen\u00e8ve","type":"date de naissance"}],"creatorRole":"Horloger","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""},{"label":"C\u00e9ret, Louis","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"","place":"Gen\u00e8ve","type":"date de naissance"}],"creatorRole":"Horloger","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 8028","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"horlogerie ; montre","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Montre ronde orn\u00e9e sur le fond du bo\u00eetier d\u0027une peinture en \u00e9mail repr\u00e9sentant Vertumne et Pomone, le pourtour grav\u00e9 de volutes est orn\u00e9 de fleurettes \u00e9maill\u00e9es bleues. Lunette grav\u00e9e de stries et de volutes, orn\u00e9e de guirlandes fleuries \u00e9maill\u00e9es. Cadran en \u00e9mail blanc avec chiffres romains et arabes, deux aiguilles en or reperc\u00e9es. Le mouvement poss\u00e8de un \u00e9chappement \u00e0 roue de rencontre, une rosette de r\u00e9glage en argent, un coq ajour\u00e9 de rinceaux. Ch\u00e2telaine non assortie, en or grav\u00e9 et repouss\u00e9 de motifs rocaille. Sur la plaque sup\u00e9rieure figure un joueur de fl\u00fbte v\u00eatu \u00e0 l\u0027antique.","inscriptions":"Inscription : \r ; Cadran sign\u00e9 : Les Dufour et Ceret\/A FERNEY\r ; Mouvement sign\u00e9 : Manufre Royale\/DE FERNEY\r ; Poin\u00e7on : \r ; Ma\u00eetre illisible (\u00e0 l\u0027int\u00e9rieur du bo\u00eetier) ; \u00e0 l\u0027int\u00e9rieur du bo\u00eetier J\/G\/ sous couronne. ; sur la ch\u00e2telaine, trois poin\u00e7ons illisibles et poin\u00e7on de Maison Commune, Paris, M couronn\u00e9 (1775-1776).","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"14,9","displayDimension":"14,9 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"4","displayDimension":"4 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Profondeur","value":"1,5","displayDimension":"1,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""},{"type":"Hauteur","value":"3,5","displayDimension":"3,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":4,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"3,2","displayDimension":"3,2 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":5,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau\/Technique : \u00e9mail peint\r\nMat\u00e9riau : or\r\nMat\u00e9riau : argent\r\nTechnique : techniques m\u00e9tal (orf\u00e8vrerie)","placeOfCreation":"Ferney-Voltaire = Ferney (Rh\u00f4ne-Alpes = Rh\u00f4ne Alpes-\u003EAin)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"collection Georges Heine (1861-1928) ; legs en 1929.","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value"